# Shrink API image build context (docker compose build api) — faster uploads and better layer cache hits.
# AppleDouble files (._*) on exFAT/external volumes break Docker buildx ("failed to xattr ... operation not permitted").
**/._*
.git
.github
.cursor
**/.venv
**/venv
**/node_modules
frontend
scraper
test-results
.pytest_cache
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
**/*.pyo
*.md
docs
.env
.env.*
